g.text: Real Mode to Protected Mode Transition

p.strong: Why the Far Jump is NOT Optional

div.p: After setting CR0.PE, the CPU is in protected mode, but the instruction prefetch queue still contains 16-bit real-mode instructions.

ol.li: CS reload from GDT (loads protected-mode selector 0x08)
Fresh instruction fetch from protected-mode code

div.p: Without it: the CPU executes garbage Triple Fault System Reset
